binarySearchTree

Class BinTree

  • java.lang.Object
    • binarySearchTree.BinTree

  • public class BinTree
extends java.lang.Object
    A class for a binary search tree data structure. This creates an empty node called root. It is used by creating BST's with each node being another BST.
    Author:
    Patrick Martinez
